### Analysis

#### Base model (H2_1)


::: {.cell filename='Main model'}

```{.r .cell-code .hidden}
#| filename: Main model
H2_model_1 <- 
  bam(H2_form_1, 
      data = metric_participanthour, 
      discrete = TRUE,
      method = "fREML",
      nthreads = 10
      )

r1 <- start_value_rho(H2_model_1, 
                      plot=TRUE)
```

